1.2
log
@Remove net/wide-dhcp.  Unmaintained code, broken on 64 bits archs.

dhclient(8) does the job for most setups and is much sa[fn]er, others
can use dhclient from net/isc-dhcp.

ok steven@@ ajacoutot@@ sthen@@
